{"tid":2356730,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【最新估價】拉豬福特成歐洲最高身價球員, 夏蘭特排第二","createTime":"2021-01-07T03:46:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-07T15:44:43.000Z","uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"656e55eacb4f78ab625592a421f1eca31c197a0c","tid":2356730,"uid":34571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T03:46:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://football-observatory.com/IMG/sites/b5wp/2020/wp319/en/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffootball-observatory.com%2FIMG%2Fsites%2Fb5wp%2F2020%2Fwp319%2Fen%2F&d=tgCcTb3Ji4LFIEkqsM1g5gOzzNjRw9ZJ5YgnvwIkb18%3D&h=ce366daa\" target=\"_blank\">https://football-observatory.com/IMG/sites/b5wp/2020/wp319/en/</a><br />\n<br />\n根據 CIES Football Observatory披露的最細數據，曼聯的拉舒福特（Marcus Rashford）是眼下球壇價值最高的球員，壓過了夏蘭特（Erling Haland）、麥巴比（Kylian Mbappe）等人。<br />\n<br />\n  拉舒福特以1.656億歐元的估值位列第一，第二是夏蘭特（1.52億歐元），第三是利物浦的阿諾特（Trent Alexander-Arnold）（1.516億歐元）。麥巴比以1.494億歐元排在第五。<br />\n<br />\n  這份估價榜單的考量因素，包括年齡、合約期、生涯進展度以及球隊成績等，麥巴比之所以估值較低，因為他和巴黎的合約期只剩18個月，而且至今沒有續約。<br />\n<br />\n  在這份榜單中，美斯的估值為5400萬歐元，排在球壇第97名，而C.朗拿度（Cristiano Ronaldo）僅以4700萬歐元的估值，排在第131位，這樣的較低估值，和兩人的年齡以及合約都快到期有很大關係。"},{"pid":"928e9ac0ee3fe177040fb31fe4b98c4d2b7ce6d0","tid":2356730,"uid":96525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T03:49:16.000Z","msg":"我福非賣"},{"pid":"59437ef4126e2aaab44fac1a912b59f70292e857","tid":2356730,"uid":18587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T03:54:28.000Z","msg":"狼隊都幾勁，個list有兩位"},{"pid":"bdcb7d3e8e0618479d4d6b6c15fb40b20440740f","tid":2356730,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T03:56:52.000Z","msg":"麥巴比踢完世盃 冇晒聲氣"},{"pid":"1b62bc49581d358468595eeead2bf5da8290083b","tid":2356730,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-07T04:19:03.000Z","msg":"MBE <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f469446a04f6d63955c02ed02993a3c57d76e